      <hedline>
        <hl1>Alone at the Top</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Stephen Leshinski letter expresses disappointment in Roger Lowenstein's August 27 profile of Sanford I Weill (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>I am disappointed that you would choose to focus on a neurotic workaholic whose claim to fame is that he makes a lot of money and fires his close friends.</p>
        <p>Stephen Leshinski  Hackensack, N.J.</p>
      </block>
